<!DOCTYPE SimulIDE>

<!--
    Generic AVR compiler entry: no local toolchain, no build steps.
    Used for non-Arduino AVR MCU drops (.c / .cpp). Actual compilation
    happens server-side via Compiler::remoteCompile; the X-Mcu-Name /
    X-Family headers tell the server which avr-gcc target to invoke.
    Pairs with GenericAvrDebugger so DWARF stepping, variable inspection,
    and disassembly work against the returned .elf — same pipeline as
    InoDebugger but without the Arduino .ino path conventions.
-->
<compiler name="Generic-AVR" type="genericavr">
</compiler>
